longBusinessSummary: Sonetel AB (publ) provides internet-based subscription service for business communication in Sweden. The company offers phone numbers, voice response, and call recording services. It provides business communication, customer service software, team communication, SIP trunking, cloud IVR, AI meeting minutes and blog writer, and API services. The company was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
